\par 
\par }{\f1 The preview image must be a Targa image that is 256 pixels wide by 110 pixels tall, again with a filename identical to the map (with a .tga extension).  Place this image in the folder: }{\b\f1 czero\\gfx\\thumbnails\\maps_wide}{\f1 .
